    public class Annotator
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.apache.thrift.TBase<Annotator,Annotator._Fields>, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<Annotator>
    An Annotator object describes a human (or possibly a set of humans) who generated the data stored in a Label or Rating object.
